Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.65,0:00:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,TRAVELOG. PCS = travel + cargo + paperwork across 3 different systems\Ntoday. One sentence in. One plan out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.65,0:00:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,LOGCOM published use cases: Travel Program Validation, TMR Automation,\NLogTRACE. TRAVELOG covers all three.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.70,0:00:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Four datasets fused into one agent: synthetic DTS, AFCENT logistics,\NBTS NTAD multimodal corridor, LaDe last-mile. No data movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.70,0:00:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A Marine PCS-ing from Lejeune to Pendleton, escorting an M1078 LMTV.\NClick View Options.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.75,0:00:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The mode optimizer compares 4 packages: fly + ship cargo, drive +\Nship, drive escorting, fly + air-freight. Time, cost, fuel, JTR …
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.76,0:00:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Submit Both — real OpenAI tool-calling fires submit_tmr and\Nprefill_dts_voucher in parallel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.78,0:00:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,DTS voucher pre-fill on the left. JTR-compliant per-diem, GTCC,\Nmode-of-travel. Cargo TMR on the right. DTR 4500.9-R compliant. …
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.79,0:01:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Same code path inside the wire. Set KAMIWAZA_BASE_URL and CUI never\Nleaves the perimeter. Air-gapped, IL5/IL6 ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.82,0:01:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Cached one-page combined action plan renders instantly. Three buttons.\NBuilt on the Kamiwaza Stack.
